ygData.messageBody:
I have been through North and South ro and have not seen any remnants of the
elvish empire as far as I can tell.

Grod

-----Original Message-----
From: Saffy Lynn [mailto:saffy@...]
Sent: Monday, May 24, 1999 3:34 PM
To: 'eqpaladin@onelist.com'
Subject: Re: [eqpaladin] New Subject-keeping group alive!--Your Server


From: Saffy Lynn <saffy@...>

I'm on the Xegony server (High Elf Paladin, level 14). I have a question
that maybe you can help me with. I have been traveling through Antonica
lately, but have not yet been to Ro. Since the Eldarr Woods used to occupy
that land before Solusek destroyed it, I am wondering if there are any
remnants of the Elvish Empire. any information would be appreciated.

thanks,
Eglath
